<h4 id="prototype">Prototype</h4>

<div class="mermaid">
  flowchart LR
    A[Class B]
    B[Class C]
    C[Class D]
    subgraph Spring Container
    D[Spring Container]
    I[Spring Container]
    J[Spring Container]
    end
    F[Instance A]
    G[Instance A']
    H[Instance A'']
    A--getBean--&gt;D
    B--getBean--&gt;I
    C--getBean--&gt;J
    D&lt;-.manage.-&gt;F
    I&lt;-.manage.-&gt;G
    J&lt;-.manage.-&gt;H
</div>

<p>Л┼╓М■└К╖│Л≈░Л└°К┼■ К≤░К▀╓К╔╦ К╧┬ Л┼╓Л╫■М■└Й╟─ Л·┬К┼■К█╟ Prototype Л┼╓Л╫■М■└Л²╢К▀╓.</p>

<p>Й╟│ Л┼╓Л╫■М■└КЁ└К║° Л╩╗М┘▄Л²╢К└┬Л≈░ Й╟²Л╡╢Й╟─ Л╟╦Л║╟К░═ К∙▄К╖┬К▀╓ Л┐┬К║°Л ╢ Л²╦Л┼╓М└╢Л┼╓Й╟─ Л┐²Л└╠К░°К▀╓.</p>

<div class="language-xml highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nt">&lt;bean</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"eye"</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"com.csupreme19.springdemo.Eye"</span> <span class="na">scope=</span><span class="s">"prototype"</span> <span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

